I'm trying to populate some fields on a form based on a select option: some are inputs, some are selects.

My problem is: when the event is triggered the value of any targeted mat-select changes, but the option selected visually disappears (even if there is an option with that value in the list).

I'm tryed to do like that:

```
setTimeout(() => {
              this.resourceForm.controls[target_field].setValue(target_value);
              this.resourceForm.controls[target_field].patchValue(target_value);
}, 10);
```

Where resourceForm is my form, target_field is the target select and target_value is the value that the select must receive.
